heif.boxes

Class ItemInformationBox3

  • java.lang.Object
    • heif.boxes.Box
      • heif.boxes.FullBox
        • heif.boxes.ItemInformationBox3

  • public class ItemInformationBox3
extends FullBox
    This derived Box class handles the Box identified as iinf - Item Information Box. For technical details, refer to the Specification document - ISO/IEC 14496-12:2015 on Page 81 to 83.

    Version History:

    • 1.0 - Initial release by Trevor Maggs on 31 May 2025
    Since:
    31 May 2025
    Author:
    Trevor Maggs
